  "review_decision": "The tracked curated reader manuscript renders locally to HTML, EPUB, DOCX, and PDF and passes structural artifact inspection. The DOCX and PDF renders use ten temporary PNG fallbacks generated from the tracked SVG key figures inside the ignored build workspace, and the PDF render now also uses 50 temporary Chrome-screenshot Mermaid fallbacks so browser-rendered diagram labels survive without clipping. The refreshed PDF all-page text/bounding-box audit checked 504 pages, 169766 word boxes, 0 textless pages, 0 out-of-bounds word boxes, 0 layout lines over 160 characters, and required text markers; the all-page raster audit reports 0 blank pages, 0 low-ink pages, and 0 near-edge pages. EPUB also has a Chromium XHTML browser review with 104 page-view pairs and 0 failures. The PDF extracted-text reading-flow review checks 504 text pages, 44 ordered chapter headings, 3 ordered appendix headings, and 0 replacement characters. EPUB, DOCX, and PDF remain unapproved because dedicated e-reader approval, DOCX application review, manual PDF viewer reading-flow/layout review, and an edition release record do not yet exist.",
